text: Elyes Fakhfakh (; born 1972) is a Tunisian politician. He was the Minister of Tourism and, starting on 19 of December 2012, as the Minister of Finances as well, under Prime Minister Hamadi Jebali.Asma Ghribi, Elyes Fakhfakh , #'Tunisia Live, 22 December 2011 He was the Prime Minister from 28 February 2020 until 2 September 2020. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1972 births Category:Politicians from Tunis Category:Prime Ministers of Tunisia
title: Elyes Fakhfakh
